  "description": "For a high-tack adhesive on both horizontal and vertical fixings, Everbuild Mammoth Multi-Purpose Double Sided Tape is the ideal pick. This double-sided 50mm tape works best in temperatures above 5°C to provide a strong bond between smooth surfaces. It doesn't matter if they are porous or not, as the high-tack properties of this tape make a grippy connection. Simply unroll what you need, tear or cut off the rest and press it into place on one material. Remove the protective film and press the two surfaces firmly together. Also available in a 5m roll and 25m roll with a 25mm width.",
